Title: The Beatles - Red & Blue Albums (2023 Edition)
Description: Remixed and Expanded: 'Red’ has 12 additional tracks, including for the first time some of George Harrison’s earliest songs and some classic Beatles versions of R&B and rock ‘n’ roll hits that were so influential on the band. ‘Blue’ has 9 additional tracks including “Blackbird,” “Glass Onion,” and the last new Beatles song, “Now And Then” for a total of 21 new additions.
